{"type":null,"faqId":9464,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00）怎样设置飞行模式？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b></span><span><span>-&gt;</span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">飞行模式</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可以打开或者关闭飞行模式。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29921\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>也可以通过按住状态栏往下拉，点击展开图标，进入查看更多的快捷方式，点击飞行模式的图标，就可以打开和关闭飞行模式。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29919\" /></span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在飞行模式下</span><span><span>,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">数据连接不可以用，可以手动再次打开</span><span><span>WLAN.</span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"63","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396253102000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":200,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"飞行模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}